{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286140/extras/promo_art.png?t=1734423666\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286140/extras/about.png?t=1734423666\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Providentia Academy is a captivating 2D visual novel that immerses players in a world of mystery, romance, and supernatural intrigue. Set within the prestigious walls of Providentia Academy, players will follow the story of a talented student who unravels the academy's hidden secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As players navigate through the story, they'll make choices that shape the protagonist's relationships, influence the plot, and determine the ultimate fate of the academy. With stunning visuals, evocative music, and a compelling narrative, Providentia Academy offers a unique and unforgettable gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>This is only the first chapter and not the full game. It serves as an introduction to a longer story, although it's still uncertain if we're going to continue this project. This game is a student project created in a period of 9 weeks.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Credits:</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Made by GEOMS Entertainment</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Saku Raitanen -</strong> Product Owner, Design, Narrative</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Essi Pirttivaara -</strong> Technology, Scrum Master, Producing &amp; Publishing</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gabriel Nwaoha -</strong> Audio, Implementation, Producing &amp; Publishing</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mairiin Kask -</strong> Art, Business</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Oliver Valtonen -</strong> Art, Q&amp;A</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Special thanks to:<strong> Tero Korpela -</strong> Technology</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286140/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734423666","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286140/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734423666","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286140/793ec3dbd2cb64621f0ea7c61cf68b87a62259f2/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734423666","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286140/793ec3dbd2cb64621f0ea7c61cf68b87a62259f2/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734423666","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Story line has horror elements. Player will see silhouette of dead body. Language contains occasional swearing. "},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286140/extras/promo_art.png?t=1734423666\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286140/extras/about.png?t=1734423666\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Providentia Academy is a captivating 2D visual novel that immerses players in a world of mystery, romance, and supernatural intrigue. Set within the prestigious walls of Providentia Academy, players will follow the story of a talented student who unravels the academy's hidden secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As players navigate through the story, they'll make choices that